          "We don't believe in one-size-fits-all. Our websites are crafted to meet your unique business needs and goals.",
        icon: 'tabler:wand',
      },
      {
        title: 'Performance Driven',
        description:
          'We build websites with speed and efficiency in mind, ensuring a seamless user experience and optimal search engine performance.',
        icon: 'tabler:bolt',
      },
      {
        title: 'Transparent Communication',
        description:
          'We keep you informed every step of the way, with clear communication and collaborative project management.',
        icon: 'tabler:message-circle',
      },
      {
        title: 'Future-Proof Technology',
        description:
          'Our websites are built using the latest technologies and best practices, ensuring scalability and adaptability for years to come.',
