      {
        testimonial: `Criztec created a fantastic e-commerce website for my vintage clothing store.  They made the online shopping experience seamless and secure.  I'm impressed with their attention to detail and commitment to customer satisfaction. I highly recommend Criztec to any small business looking to grow online!`,
